{"tid":533912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"21萬人住劏房　三成屬青年","createTime":"2018-01-19T09:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T11:01:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8877b57ea933e342c41bd1342f79ba1394356854","tid":533912,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180119/20279092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F20279092&d=O%2FDIUHGNus3%2BZXxg%2BPUTdfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6167dde4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F20279092&h=e7cb10b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180119/20279092</a><br />\n<br />\n21萬人住劏房　三成屬青年<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180119/large/1516293945_0ceb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180119%2Flarge%2F1516293945_0ceb.jpg&h=0030085a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】統計處昨發表《2016年中期人口統計主題性報告：居於分間樓宇單位人士》報告。根據2016年中期人口統計結果，全港估計約有92,700個劏房，居民人數為209,700人，較2015年分別增加4%及5%，當中約三成屬25歲以下青年，劏房集中地仍是油尖旺及深水埗區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n居住環境惡化　租金升<br />\n<br />\n調查顯示劏房居住環境惡化，2016年劏房每戶平均住2.3人，比一年前平均2人多，但劏房面積中位數由10.3平方米下降至10平方米，人均面積亦由5.8平方米減至5.3平方米。劏房租金中位數則上升7%至4,500元。調查又顯示，2016年劏房居民中，28.4%為25歲以下，39.4%為25至44歲，24.0%為45至64歲，而65歲及以上人士佔8.2%。<br />\n<br />\n2016年劏房戶月收入中位數為13,500元，比一年前升8%，但仍低於全港家庭住戶中位數25,000元。27%人從事住宿及膳食服務業、19.5%從事進出口、批發及零售業，但劏房居民學歷有升勢，12.7%具專上教育程度，比一年前8.1%多4個百分點，具中學程度劏房居民亦由60.3%上升70%。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮"},{"pid":"1c2a937a938282a99a049ccdd60224094d25b765","tid":533912,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:44:11.000Z","msg":"我就係其中之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fa4f2ebb148a34e534848555f11fe16cc37ee3","tid":533912,"uid":53866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"我就係三成其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fafb645a03a4c894c03b4cabc80fb9eb84a13dfb","tid":533912,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f38689ff8e3923a37406e78a4c472163da04d95f","tid":533912,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:51:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8677db065c598aed1e95069dadaeabafafaee591","tid":533912,"uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"Fucking Hong Kong"},{"pid":"d38fa03b5dec543b64988cf832e433a930459024","tid":533912,"uid":131020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:05:51.000Z","msg":"我樓下有劏房得60尺左右,但一個人同隻大狗住,細到狗屎盤都唔知放邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d526623d663b89b14ee9736d50aa0acdca09741","tid":533912,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"我就嚟係其中一份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5433fa6768648a3f1ea04c77eff49e08edacb070","tid":533912,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303d15fe935f0c0b16b3b51378de6fc39b56d751","tid":533912,"uid":33022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母香港政府"},{"pid":"05bcc9a909c577e6350c15ab3feda6a008bafdbd","tid":533912,"uid":48286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"香港年青人特別 折墮"},{"pid":"61fa0ad0e1ab4f6b3b0d0ae0b86d26601975e845","tid":533912,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"